    <td class="content" valign="top"><!-- InstanceBeginEditable name="main content" --><a id="top"></a> 
<h1 class="homepage">Achieving best practice – we have merged with businesslink.gov.uk</h1>
<p class="home-text"> To provide you with improved access to <em>Achieving best practice in your business </em>information, we've merged our content and services with the DTI-backed national Business Link portal.</p>

<p class="home-text">For easy, practical support and guidance in achieving best practice in your business, please visit any of the following areas:</p> 
<ul class="homepage">

<li>
<a href="http://www.businesslink.gov.uk/bdotg/action/layer;jsessionid=CLvf8rdG271LK6ThMGVJ3SkYdBsS88QXTsZTLxZZxVDySjZTbhXy%21829443873%211120644959691?topicId=1074404796&amp;r.t=ONEOFFPAGE&amp;r.i=1075427049&amp;r.s=e" title="Grow your business to maturity">Grow your business</a>
</li>

<li>
<a href="http://www.businesslink.gov.uk/bdotg/action/layer;jsessionid=CLvf8rdG271LK6ThMGVJ3SkYdBsS88QXTsZTLxZZxVDySjZTbhXy%21829443873%211120644959691?topicId=1073861169&amp;r.t=ONEOFFPAGE&amp;r.i=1075427049&amp;r.s=e" title="Win customers and sell more">Sales and marketing</a>
</li>

<li>
<a href="http://www.businesslink.gov.uk/bdotg/action/layer;jsessionid=CLvf8rdG271LK6ThMGVJ3SkYdBsS88QXTsZTLxZZxVDySjZTbhXy%21829443873%211120644959691?topicId=1073858787&amp;r.t=ONEOFFPAGE&amp;r.i=1075427049&amp;r.s=e" title="Recruit, train and manage your staff">Employing people</a>
</li>

<li>
<a href="http://www.businesslink.gov.uk/bdotg/action/layer;jsessionid=CLvf8rdG271LK6ThMGVJ3SkYdBsS88QXTsZTLxZZxVDySjZTbhXy%21829443873%211120644959691?topicId=1073858796&amp;r.t=ONEOFFPAGE&amp;r.i=1075427049&amp;r.s=e" title="Develop, exploit and protect your ideas">Exploit your ideas</a>
</li>

<li>
<a href="http://www.businesslink.gov.uk/bdotg/action/layer;jsessionid=CLvf8rdG271LK6ThMGVJ3SkYdBsS88QXTsZTLxZZxVDySjZTbhXy%21829443873%211120644959691?topicId=1073861197&amp;r.t=ONEOFFPAGE&amp;r.i=1075427049&amp;r.s=e" title="Choose the right systems and suppliers">IT &amp; e-commerce</a>
</li>
</ul>

<p class="home-text"> By <a href="https://www.businesslink.gov.uk/bdotg/action/register?tc=000AD120160078">registering</a> with the Business Link web site, you can join the 800,000 people involved in businesses that visit the site each month and take advantage of:</p>
<ul class="homepage"><li>430 plain English guides and more than 25 interactive tools, helping you to understand a wide range of best practice and business issues.</li>
         <li>A Grants and Support Directory of over 2,800 potential sources of help, with particular schemes targeted at achieving best practice in your business.</li>
         <li>Over 120 real life case studies illustrating how businesses have implemented best practice for themselves.</li>
</ul>
<p class="home-text"><a href="https://www.businesslink.gov.uk/bdotg/action/register?tc=000AD120160078">Registering</a>  with Business Link is completely free, confidential and takes less than a minute to complete. </p>
<!--<p class="home-text">Some <em>Achieving best practice in your business </em> website tools, such as the <a href="http://www.dti-bestpractice-tools.org/planner/login.jsp">E-business planner</a>  and the <a href="http://www.dti-bestpractice-tools.org/benchmark/">Technology benchmarking</a> tools, are being considered for delivery via businesslink.gov.uk soon. Further tools will be added during the course of the year. </p>-->
<p class="home-text">To find out more about how the Business Link website can help you achieve best practice in your business, visit <a href="http://www.businesslink.gov.uk/abp?tc=000AD120160077">www.businesslink.gov.uk/abp</a>.</p>

<br />

        
